Quest Software and Applications

This page provides a self-service, interactive tool to search for software and applications commonly used on Quest, the Universityâ€™s high-performance computing cluster. Choose to search by name or explore your options using various filtering criteria. Click on any item in the software and applications list to expand a dropdown and view more details.

Please note that this Quest software and applications list is subject to change, and additional software not listed here may be available. Please log into Quest and run the command module available for the complete list. Except where noted, the Modules Software Environment Manager must be used to set up your environment to use the Quest software.
